subject: Pro Bowl
Football
lead_paragraph: Larry Fitzgerald caught five passes for 81 yards and 2 touchdowns, John Carney, 44, kicked two fourth-quarter field goals, and the N.F.C. rallied for a 30-21 victory over the A.F.C. on Sunday in the Pro Bowl in Honolulu.
